author: wn.com
title: Jim Webb may be contemplating running as an independent instead of as a Democrat
text: RICHMOND — Jim Webb announced Monday that he is thinking about turning his Democratic bid for president into an independent one. " Jim Webb to Consider Independent Run, " the campaign said Monday in an e-mailed statement. Webb is scheduled to hold a news conference about his plans in Washington on Tuesday.
